description:
Triumvirate Character Pack (TCP)
By Blackwater

Adds the following skins to the following bots:
* Aphid: Sonaphid (Based on Sona from the Undertale Kissy Cutie fangame)
* Router: UM1 (Based on Umi the Umriss Girl)
* Tachi: AZPT (Based on Lizzy the Azzypants Fujoshi)

All skins are unlocked by default.
name: TCP
